nodes.text: Cal was a Human male who was part of the Wolf Squadron Rebel unit during the Galactic Civil War.

Cal's squadron operated from the planetoid Annamar, hidden deep within a massive asteroid field near the Corellian Trade Spine.
During the Battle of Annamar, Cal fought against Darth Vader, firing on him with a blaster rifle. He and his squadron were all killed when Vader dropped a BTL Y-wing starfighter on the starfighters stationed in the base.
